The estimates of the daily ECR for each of the seven countries, together with their 95% confidence intervals, are provided in Fig. 3. The profiles of the corresponding effective reproduction number are presented in Fig. S1.
Fig. 3
ECR profiles per country. The trend in the point estimates of the ECR \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
